ygData.msgSnippet: He is decked out in full plate and carries two ice picks.  I read on some board somewhere that he had some nice items, they just didn t list them.
ygData.messageBody:
He is decked out in full plate and carries two ice picks. I read
on some board somewhere that he had some nice items, they
just didn't list them.
